com.streambase.sbunit.ext.matchers

Interface IgnoreNullTransform

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ValueMatcher
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FieldBasedTupleMatcher, ListValueMatcher, NullValueMatcher

    public interface IgnoreNullTransform
extends ValueMatcher
    This interface is used to control structural recursion of ValueMatchers when creating a new version of them that ignores nulls values.
